attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Gold Key Realty, Inc.

data.description: Amazing investment, house-hack, or owner-occupy opportunity! This 0.39 acre property boasts a legal duplex, a separate detached single family home, and 2000+ sq ft workshop with attached one-car garage!  The duplex has very large living rooms, with two bedrooms on the main floor, two upstairs, and one extra large bedroom in the basement unit. Each unit comes with new, matching GE washer and dryer sets. The detached SFR is a one bed, one bath home. One of the most profitable multi-family properties on the market, gross rents for this property are an impressive $4,300 per month and could be raised with additional improvements to the property! Separate Meters; tenants pay most utilities. This property is highly desirable for students attending Utah State University or those looking to specifically live in the "Island" neighborhood of Logan.
